<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8057383>
    dc:description "Figures 8–15. Wing venation from representative species of Anthophorini. 8. Anthophora (Lophanthophora) dammersi Timberlake. 9. Amegilla quadrifasciata (de Villers). 10. Habropoda depressa Fowler. 11. Elaphropoda percarinata (Cockerell). 12. Pachymelus (Pachymelus) unicolor (Saussure). 13. Deltoptila sp. 14. Habrophorula nubilipennis (Cockerell). 15. Varthemapistra edentata, new genus and species." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8057383/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

